prediction.sparql:
PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
PREFIX imdb: <https://www.imdb.com/>
SELECT ?series ?label ( COUNT( ?episode ) AS ?numEpisodes ) WHERE {
  ?series imdb:titleType "tvSeries" .
  ?series imdb:numVotes ?votes .
  FILTER ( ?votes > 1000000 ) OPTIONAL {
    ?series rdfs:label ?label
  }
  ?episode imdb:titleType "tvEpisode" .
  ?episode imdb:parentTitle ?series .
}
GROUP BY ?series ?label
ORDER BY DESC ( ?numEpisodes )
LIMIT 5

PREFIX xsd: <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#>
PREFIX imdb: <https://www.imdb.com/>
SELECT ?decade ( AVG( ?rating ) AS ?avgRating ) ( COUNT( ?movie ) AS ?numMovies ) WHERE {
  ?movie imdb:genre "Sci-Fi" .
  ?movie imdb:titleType "movie" .
  ?movie imdb:averageRating ?rating .
  ?movie imdb:numVotes ?votes .
  ?movie imdb:startYear ?year .
  FILTER ( ?votes > 10000 ) FILTER ( xsd:integer ( ?year ) > 1800 ) BIND( FLOOR( xsd:integer ( ?year ) / 10 ) * 10 AS ?decade )
}
GROUP BY ?decade
ORDER BY ?decade

PREFIX imdb: <https://www.imdb.com/>
PREFIX imdb_principal: <https://www.imdb.com/principal/>
SELECT ?director ?movie ?rating ?votes WHERE {
  ?movie imdb:titleType "movie" .
  ?movie imdb_principal:director ?director .
  ?movie imdb:numVotes ?votes .
  ?movie imdb:averageRating ?rating .
  FILTER ( ?votes >= 100000 ) {
    SELECT ?director ( MAX( ?rating ) AS ?maxRating ) WHERE {
      ?movie imdb:titleType "movie" .
      ?movie imdb_principal:director ?director .
      ?movie imdb:numVotes ?votes .
      ?movie imdb:averageRating ?rating .
      FILTER ( ?votes >= 100000 )
    }
    GROUP BY ?director
  }
  FILTER ( ?rating = ?maxRating )
}
ORDER BY DESC ( ?rating ) DESC ( ?votes )
LIMIT 10

PREFIX imdb: <https://www.imdb.com/>
SELECT ?person ( AVG( ?votes ) AS ?avgVotes ) ( COUNT( ?title ) AS ?numTitles ) WHERE {
  ?person imdb:knownForTitle ?title .
  ?title imdb:numVotes ?votes .
}
GROUP BY ?person
HAVING ( COUNT( ?title ) >= 3 )
ORDER BY DESC ( ?avgVotes )
LIMIT 10

PREFIX imdb: <https://www.imdb.com/>
SELECT ?movie ?director ?directorBirthYear ?releaseYear ?votes ( ( ?releaseYear - ?directorBirthYear ) AS ?ageAtRelease ) WHERE {
  ?movie imdb:numVotes ?votes .
  FILTER ( ?votes > 1000000 ) ?movie imdb:director ?director .
  ?movie imdb:startYear ?releaseYear .
  ?director imdb:birthYear ?directorBirthYear .
}
ORDER BY ASC ( ?ageAtRelease )
LIMIT 1

PREFIX imdb: <https://www.imdb.com/>
SELECT ?genre ( COUNT( DISTINCT ?title ) AS ?frequency ) ( AVG( ?rating ) AS ?averageRating ) WHERE {
  ?title imdb:genre ?genre .
  ?title imdb:averageRating ?rating .
}
GROUP BY ?genre
ORDER BY DESC ( ?frequency )

PREFIX imdb: <https://www.imdb.com/>
SELECT ?person ( COUNT( DISTINCT ?title ) AS ?numTitles ) WHERE {
  ?person imdb:knownForTitle ?title .
  ?title imdb:numVotes ?votes .
  FILTER ( ?votes > 1000000 )
}
GROUP BY ?person
HAVING ( COUNT( DISTINCT ?title ) >= 3 )
ORDER BY DESC ( ?numTitles )
LIMIT 100
